{"type":"message","id":"8b39cb95","parentId":"4924e254","timestamp":"2026-03-22T02:54:38.106Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The disk filled up - \"Disk quota exceeded\". The model is 24.8GB + 69.4GB + other files, and the machine only has 150GB. We downloaded Q4_K_M.gguf (24.8GB) and Q5_K_M.gguf (69.4GB)... wait, that's huge. Actually looking more carefully, it seems like the Q4_K_M was 24.8GB and Q5_K_M was 69.4GB? That doesn't seem right for a quantized model.\n\nWait, actually it says \"Download complete. Moving file to /notebooks/model/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B-Uncensored-HauhauCS-Aggressive-Q4_K_M.gguf 130MB/s\" then \"Qwen3.5-35B-A3B-Uncensored-HauhauCS-Aggr(…): 100%|███████████████████████████████| 24.8G/24.8G [04:46<00:00, 86.3MB/s]\" then \"Download complete. Moving file to /notebooks/model/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B-Uncensored-HauhauCS-Aggressive-Q5_K_M.gguf 143MB/s\" and then the Q5_K_M shows 69.4G which is the total.\n \nLooking at the download pattern, it seems like the repo contains multiple model files (Q4_K_M.gguf, Q5_K_M.gguf) and they're all being downloaded, which exhausted the disk. The simplest fix is to delete the partial download and just target the specific Q4_K_M file we actually need, since that's the 20GB quant we planned to use.","thinkingSignature":"40ec440502272dcac4d780b719521c212fbe88a706f37e84032501016656e455"},{"type":"text","text":"Disk filled up — \"Disk quota exceeded\". The model repo has multiple quantized variants and Paperspace ran out of space.\n\nClean it up and grab just the Q4_K_M file:\n\n```\nrm -rf /notebooks/model\nhuggingface-cli download HauhauCS/Qwen3.5-35B-A3B-Uncensored-HauhauCS-Aggressive --local-dir /notebooks/model --include \"*Q4_K_M*\"\n```\n\nThat's the ~20GB Q4 quant we actually need. Skip the Q5_K_M and FP8 variants — they won't fit on 150GB anyway."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":482,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":38248,"totalTokens":38773,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774148063805}}
