{"type":"message","id":"c217698c","parentId":"e5db1631","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:59:52.753Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is taking too long. Let me just focus on what matters. The notebook web UI is returning \"Service Unavailable\". This means the container is either:1. Stopped (not running)\n2. Running but the web service is down\n3. Network issue between my location and Paperspace\n\nSince I can't restart the notebook through an API, and the Paperspace CLI isn't installed, and SSH is blocked...I need to be honest with Zach. The notebook is inaccessible from my end, and I don't have the right tools to manage Paperspace from here.\n\nThe best path forward:\n1. Have Zach restart the notebook from paperspace.com console\n2. Once it's back up, I can try to run the model deployment commands through the Jupyter cell mechanism\n\nOr alternatively:\n\n\n3. Use the OpenClaw coding-agent skill to spin up a Codex/Claude Code session on Paperspace directly, which would let me execute commands without needing the CLI or SSH access.\n\nLet me present both options to Zach clearly.","thinkingSignature":"4d4f290a5877972d7ec03f687f006230842fbb8a1dd753c1ce62578a1be734a3"},{"type":"text","text":"SSH and all ports on Paperspace are blocked from outside — the container's network is isolated. The notebook UI also returning \"Service Unavailable\" suggests the container is either stopped or the web service is down.\n\n**Real options:**\n\n1. **You restart the notebook** at `console.paperspace.com` → it takes 2 min → then I can deploy from here\n2. **Codex/Claude Code on Paperspace** — once the notebook is running, I can spawn a coding agent directly inside the Paperspace environment to finish the setup\n\nThe cleanest path: you click \"Start\" on the notebook in the Paperspace console. Then I can run everything from here through the notebook cell execution or a sub-agent.\n\nCan you start it from the console?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":53482,"output":364,"cacheRead":12408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66254,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774151979063}}
